(252, 1, '2015-09-02 10:17:05', '2015-09-02 10:17:05', '<h5 class="stitle">These processes, we can look after you</h5>\r\n<div id="Haalbaarheid" class="service-item">\r\n<div class="title"><img src="http://localhost/PHP/BLISS/COMACON/source/www/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/s-question.png" alt="" />Feasibility</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We put together with an architect to undertake an assessment of gaps in coverage conduct to purchase building plots.</li>\r\n	<li>We make a feasibility and efficiency calculation of your potential project in accordance with your vision and strategy.</li>\r\n	<li>The construction cost estimate is worked out in detail as already briefly certain material choices and sums</li>\r\n	<li>We will check your own specific sales prices and advise you.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="Ontwerp" class="service-item">\r\n<div class="title"><img src="http://localhost/PHP/BLISS/COMACON/source/www/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/s-pen.png" alt="" />Design</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We propose a general planning of all the processes that will be followed.</li>\r\n	<li>We enjoy working with our team on together and discuss the preliminary function of the construction cost estimate and</li>\r\n	<li>The team checks are specific points stability and EPB in function of agreed construction method</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="Prijsaanvragen" class="service-item">\r\n<div class="title"><img src="http://localhost/PHP/BLISS/COMACON/source/www/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/s-book.png" alt="" />Price Request</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We propose a general planning of all the processes that will be followed.</li>\r\n	<li>We enjoy working with our team on together and discuss the preliminary function of the construction cost estimate and</li>\r\n	<li>The team checks are specific points stability and EPB in function of agreed construction method</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="Bestelling" class="service-item">\r\n<div class="title"><img src="http://localhost/PHP/BLISS/COMACON/source/www/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/s-note.png" alt="" />Order</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We will inform you which party is appropriate in our view to your project and guide you to take this lump so you will be placed later for no additional budgetary surprises.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="Uitvoering" class="service-item">\r\n<div class="title"><img src="http://localhost/PHP/BLISS/COMACON/source/www/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/s-hat.png" alt="" />Execution</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We follow the wharf in your name via a digital online system to realize your dream result within schedule and budget.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="Verkoop-marketing" class="service-item">\r\n<div class="title"><img src="http://localhost/PHP/BLISS/COMACON/source/www/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/s-euro.png" alt="" />Verkoop en marketing</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Make a market research and sales pricing in terms of net yield</li>\r\n	<li>Checking design in terms of marketability.</li>\r\n	<li>Sales strategy and marketing budget determine ranging from 3D to promotional films</li>\r\n	<li>Follow Up and adjust strategy</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'Building Promoters / Investors', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'building-promoters-investors', '', '', '2015-09-02 15:15:58', '2015-09-02 15:15:58', '', 244, 'http://localhost/PHP/BLISS/www/YVES/COMACON/sourcecode/BE/?page_id=252', 0, 'page', '', 0),
