(313, 1, '2015-09-02 12:49:38', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Usted tiene una disposición de la tierra y no sabe qué hacer aquí?\nPodemos ayudarle en este documento para discutir con usted cuáles son las opciones y lo que para evaluar el suelo a un valor apropiado.\nLuego nos guiamos para empujar a través del suelo\nVemos a él que la propuesta aborda correctamente en una situación ganar - ganar.', 'Los propietarios de tierras', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', '', '', '', '2015-09-02 12:49:38', '2015-09-02 12:49:38', '', 0, 'http://localhost/PHP/BLISS/www/YVES/COMACON/sourcecode/BE/?post_type=news&#038;p=313', 0, 'news', '', 0),
(314, 1, '2015-09-02 12:54:06', '2015-09-02 12:54:06', '<h5 class="page-box__title text-uppercase">Comacon construction coordination</h5>\r\nComacon is a management and consulting firm has grown from 15 years of experience and knowledge within the world of construction and real estate.\r\n\r\nComacon guides in a transparent and open way, your residential and industrial construction projects safely and on schedule through the many processes ranging from land acquisition to implementation.\r\n\r\nA winning team of professionals is formed according to your interests and values ​​so that your project can be best achieved in a .... atmosphere\r\n\r\nDuring the entire process is a transparent online tracking relevant documents, planning and budgets allowing you at any time can follow the current state of affairs.\r\n\r\nComacon strives for innovation, speed and sustainability within your projects. We believe that these aspects play in your future positioning within the ever more rapidly changing market.\r\n\r\nOur mission is to relieve you of all the specific processes what a project entails so you can focus 100% on your core business.', 'Intro homepage', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'intro-homepage-en', '', '', '2015-09-02 13:00:23', '2015-09-02 13:00:23', '', 0, 'http://localhost/PHP/BLISS/www/YVES/COMACON/sourcecode/BE/?page_id=314', 0, 'page', '', 0),
